            <fr:title text="Alternative definition of countability">Alternative definition of <fr:link href="jms-00MH.xml" title="Countable set" addr="jms-00MH" type="local">countability</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>A set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00MH.xml" title="Countable set" addr="jms-00MH" type="local">countable</fr:link> if and only if the disjoint union <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00ME.xml" title="Enumerable set" addr="jms-00ME" type="local">enumerable</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
