 <html:p>Suppose that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00MH.xml" title="Countable set" addr="jms-00MH" type="local">countable</fr:link>. We must find a <fr:link href="jms-00M8.xml" title="Surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjection</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>; if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty, this is the same as to find a <fr:link href="jms-00M8.xml" title="Surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjection</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {N}\to {\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, which we have by <fr:link href="jms-00MA.xml" title="Non-empty sets and surjections" addr="jms-00MA" type="local">Example <fr:contextual-number addr="jms-00MA" /></fr:link>. On the other hand, if we have an enumeration <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[e\colon \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow {A}]]></fr:tex>, we may define an enumeration <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[e'\colon \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> as follows:</html:p>
 <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {aligned}
  e'{\mathopen {}\left (0\right )\mathclose {}} &= 0\\
  e'{\mathopen {}\left (n+1\right )\mathclose {}} &= e{\mathopen {}\left (n\right )\mathclose {}}
  \end {aligned}
 ]]></fr:tex>

 <html:p>Conversely, suppose that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00ME.xml" title="Enumerable set" addr="jms-00ME" type="local">enumerable</fr:link> by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[e\colon \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>. If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty, we are done. If to the contrary <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is inhabited by some <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a_0]]></fr:tex>, we let define <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[e'\colon  \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A]]></fr:tex> as follows:</html:p>
 <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
  e'{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}} =
  \begin {cases}
   e{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}} &\text {when } e{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}}\in  A\\
   a_0 &\text {otherwise}
  \end {cases}
 ]]></fr:tex>
